{"id": "1418234110345875546", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "どの陣営やりたいか決めてそのガチャ引けるとこまで引いて足りないとこで使うといいですよ", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T13:56:01.422000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1082986124441554994"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1418230990358450207", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1418237480460619918", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "355994607147941888", "author_name": "akapan_", "author_bot": false, "content": "時の起点のアイテム\n使い道分かりません。\n育てたけど、やっぱ使わないキャラ分解して育成アイテム回収以外で、例えば育ててないけど凸したキャラに使っても意味なくないですか？", "timestamp": "2025-09-18T14:09:24.920000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
